                        <interp inst="t18470614-1511-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="lesserOffence"></interp>GUILTY <hi rend="italic">of a common assault.</hi>
                     </rs>
                  </hi>  Aged 32.—<hi rend="italic">
